Show HN: Shipmunk, a universal iOS app to help you bookmark favorite apps
text:
Hi everyone, after months of hard work and beta testing, today I'm and khuong291 happy to share that Shipmunk is available to download https://apps.apple.com/app/id1638481575

As Apple fans, we're always on the outlook for cool apps to both enjoy and learn, but it can be tedious to switch stores, translate descriptions and note apps.

So we made Shipmunk, a very handy app manager to let you browse app per country with their own localized content, ratings across iOS and Mac platforms.

Features:

- Browse apps per regions.

- Favorite regions

- Add list to bookmark apps

- Use share action to add an app to Shipmunk

- ASO tracking. Shipmunk allows you to add unlimited keyword tracking across categories and platforms and see how well they perform over days.

- For developers, Shipmunk allows you to add multiple Connect accounts, see app versions information.

- Manage your own apps ratings, translate, bookmark and respond to reviews.

- More features are in the work

Hope you find the app useful.

For more information you can visit https://onmyway133.com/shipmunk/ and check out updates https://twitter.com/ShipmunkApp

Have a wonderful weekend
